{"id": "1247722992633516124", "channel_id": "1247722992633516124", "type": 0, "author_id": "943113632433197108", "author_name": "pray_unbeliever", "author_bot": false, "content": "買完注意到銀芯欄位沒跳紅點，點進去看發現到數字還是一樣。\n嘗試手動換才發現要轉換銀芯才會計入，再去確認兌換規則之後才發現必須[源液轉銀芯]才會計數，直接消耗源液是不會計算的。\n\n在我的觀點內這個捐獻基金等同於雀魂那種累積課金送東西的那種，而不是課金都課下去了還要限制你的消費模式才會計入捐獻。\n如果僅侷限於源液轉銀芯才會計入數字，我覺得用源液購買禮包的時候會感覺自己虧大了。\n希望可以把買禮包消耗的源液計入捐獻裡。\n下圖是買了流域禮包（980源液），源液變動但捐獻沒動的圖。", "timestamp": "2024-06-05T01:25:43.016000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1247722992922791977", "filename": "Screenshot_20240605_092248.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 114280, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247722992633516124/1247722992922791977/Screenshot_20240605_092248.jpg?ex=6a008757&is=69ff35d7&hm=17797940eb983ace7c093235ad97d55f48fc07c3916e29567b51bc6a91a012cc&"}, {"id": "1247722993199743117", "filename": "Screenshot_20240605_092346.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 149597, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247722992633516124/1247722993199743117/Screenshot_20240605_092346.jpg?ex=6a008757&is=69ff35d7&hm=2282507aca68e6b9aac69e1d11d9633b43a14df2a15928df602f6791744cd818&"}, {"id": "1247722993464115310", "filename": "Screenshot_20240605_092203.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 108643, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247722992633516124/1247722993464115310/Screenshot_20240605_092203.jpg?ex=6a008757&is=69ff35d7&hm=ccfa2f83d6b6aef2fe74c947fbc3d9daceca843de57004bcce5e9ae1ff21f7b5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247722992633516124", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "購買禮包所消耗的源液不會計入捐獻裡", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
